WP Data Request Cc I am working with Ray Kindley on this matter I am replying for PGP and its members who are parties to the rate case including Seattle City Light We received a hard copy of your three data requests regarding the Joint Customer Testimony on either Saturday March th or Monday March th We failed to date stamp initially which is why I am not sure which day we received it Today I received amended versions of those data requests Because of the confusion I intend to respond only to the amended version on Tuesday March th which splits the difference between the initial and the amended version due dates Please let me know if there is any problem with handling the responses in this manner Thank you in advance for your courtsey Jay T Waldron Kelly C Beniga kbeniga schwabecom NOTICE This communication may contain privileged or other confidential information If you are not the intended recipient or believe that you may have received this communication in error please reply to the sender indicating that fact and delete the copy you received In addition you should not print copy retransmit disseminate or otherwise use the information Thank you
